{"tid":1227049,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子太古廣場掛反送中橫額示威　消防拯救不果墮樓重創","createTime":"2019-06-15T14:24:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T07:43:44.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"76bb3b0757ca568e4648257a7dfd09083209199c","tid":1227049,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:24:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190615/59719455\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190615%2F59719455&d=1pbl5WvK8XMTdm%2FDcZs%2FeHza4IX%2BHJq2V8VgSm%2B5QfQ%3D&h=c4738f64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190615%2F59719455&h=7e249f62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190615/59719455</a>"},{"pid":"1c58d7bb943a0301afd60c38ed187bbeb34d1497","tid":1227049,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:26:07.000Z","msg":"唔好啊。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad0c9f2a6aad9cea7d7de3b2541fcfd5df11381","tid":1227049,"uid":123050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:28:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>行政機關濫用權力之審判</strong></span><br />\n二戰末期，納粹德國敗局已現，佛斯曼醫師、門格勒、拉舍爾三人的命運也隨著戰爭快速流轉。1945年時，拉舍爾因犯罪而被處死，和被他殺死的許多人一樣，葬身於達豪集中營裡。而門格勒假扮成一般士兵，躲過追緝後流亡到南美洲，直到1979年在巴西意外溺斃後才被確認身分。而始終堅持人性的佛斯曼醫師則在戰火中存活了下來，1945年時游過易北河後向美軍投降，戰後以泌尿科醫師的身份默默地生活著。在惡魔的年代結束之際，三名醫師分別擁來了他們各自的結局&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/5bd929a85b8a970c9c8fd7567b295223-e1450778342448.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpansci.asia%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F12%2F5bd929a85b8a970c9c8fd7567b295223-e1450778342448.jpg&h=327c7f1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左上圖：將人浸入冰水當中，藉此研究在低溫下人體的反應；左下圖：故意讓小孩感染結核菌，並切除腋下的淋巴腺，測試人體的免疫力；右圖：紐倫堡審判中，對卡爾&middot;勃蘭特（Karl Brandt）醫師的審判，他被控同意並參與非人道實驗和其他戰爭罪行，最後被判絞刑。<br />\n用屍體換來的規範－紐倫堡守則<br />\n堆積如山的屍體、骨瘦如柴的幸存者，那些泯滅人性的實驗震撼了全世界。1948年在紐倫堡進行的醫師審判，被告的醫師之中，不乏知名的科學家，如施靈（Klaus Karl Schilling）曾是國際瘧疾研究聯盟的成員，戰時卻刻意讓一千多名囚犯感染瘧疾來進行科學研究。科學家在戰爭期間荒唐的行徑，讓美國醫師里昂&middot;亞歷山大（Leo Alexander）動筆起草人體實驗中應有的道德規範，也就是今日我們熟知的「紐倫堡公約」，寫明了醫師在任何情況之下，都不得傷害受試者（除非受試者就是醫師本人）。而1964年在芬蘭舉辦的全球醫師大會更提出「赫爾辛基宣言（The Declaration of Helsinki）」，說明了受試者有絕對的權利了解實驗內容，保障了受試者「知情同意」的權益。數十年的努力之下，美國和其他國家都誓言杜絕非人道的臨床實驗，全世界都認為這種惡魔般的人體實驗不會再出現了&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qp60jU2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqp60jU2.png&h=0f218e09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/62254048_1233250940184671_5825174709460795392_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=af8a127ef43e169c16b9bc1668a17909&amp;oe=5D8A89DA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F62254048_1233250940184671_5825174709460795392_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3Daf8a127ef43e169c16b9bc1668a17909%26oe%3D5D8A89DA&h=582c6bc5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7194468e767d3eb719211e49c85529e5c6243b6d","tid":1227049,"uid":46910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:40:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8d30d9ec3dc527474745579770561fc9f4d6cb2","tid":1227049,"uid":256014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:43:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">　　睇過</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">條</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">片，</span>墮樓<span style=\"color: green;\">男子</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">當時</span><span style=\"color: red;\">十分激動，</span>不理會<span style=\"color: green;\">消防員，</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">而</span><span style=\"color: green;\">消防員</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">好像</span><span style=\"color: red;\">趕收工，大力扯</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">該名</span><span style=\"color: green;\">男子</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">上去，</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">使到</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">該名</span><span style=\"color: green;\">男子</span>不夠空間又捉不住而失足，<span style=\"color: brown;\">根據</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">畫面</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">顯示，</span><span style=\"color: green;\">地面</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">有</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">氣墊，</span>都墊不起<span style=\"color: green;\">死者，</span><br />\n<br />\n　　不知道<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">當時</span><span style=\"color: green;\">消防員</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">怎樣</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">談判，</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">而</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">畫面</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">拍到</span><span style=\"color: green;\">鄺俊宇議員</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">距離</span><span style=\"color: green;\">死者</span><span style=\"color: red;\">事發</span><span style=\"color: green;\">地點</span><span style=\"color: red;\">比較遠，</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">如果</span><span style=\"color: green;\">他</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">上去</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">談判，</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">會不會</span><span style=\"color: red;\">改寫命運？</span><br />\n<br />\n　　反送中<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">現在</span><span style=\"color: red;\">搞出了人命，</span><span style=\"color: green;\">我</span><span style=\"color: red;\">亦</span>看不到<span style=\"color: green;\">林鄭月娥</span>條死八婆<span style=\"color: brown;\">會</span><span style=\"color: red;\">關注</span>（不知道<span style=\"color: green;\">她</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">是不是</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">說：「</span>天公地義 理所當然」這八個大字）。</strong></span>"}]}